content.text:
Upon completion of the Get Log Page command, the controller posts a completion queue entry to the Admin
Completion Queue. Get Log Page command specific status values are defined in Figure 321.

tables.title: Table_5_2_12_4_Command_Completion
tables.table_md:
| Value | Definition |
|---|---|
| 9h | Invalid Log Page: The log page indicated is invalid or not supported. This error condition is also returned if a reserved log page is requested. Controllers compliant with NVM Express Base Specification revision 2.2 and earlier may return Invalid Field in Command for this condition. |
| 29h | I/O Command Set Not Supported: The specified I/O Command Set is not supported by the controller. |
